g.text: Questionnaire/DemoAs we met the client/users, we had certain set of questionnaires mentioned to probe and direct the conversations in specific direction. The process was either one-to-one or a round table discussion.
WhiteboardingWhile we did interviews or discussions, we used online whiteboard, to have a collaborative discussion, where client also got to add their views/ pointers.
Validate our findingsAfter the discovery phase, we invited the client or user to look at our findings and verified our understanding with them, eventually leading to clarity towards the requirements.
